profile:
For over 15 years Smart Roofing Inc. has provided full service roofing for residential, commercial and industrial customers throughout the Greater Toronto Area. Our skilled, experienced craftsmen, aided by the reliable products, can accurately assess your roofing situation and expedite any job quickly and to your full satisfaction. 

We are dedicated to providing quality, professional installation and service commitment with fair prices. For your protection we are fully insured, bonded and licensed, and are proud members of the Better Business Bureau. We offer from 6 to 15-year written guarantee on our workmanship and only experienced crews of roofers are used. Smart Roofing has maintained these standards over the years and will continue to do such as our family of satisfied customers grows and shares their experience with peers, family and friends. 

Please contact us today for a free estimate or visit our showroom. At Smart Roofing Inc. "We protect what you value most". Make the SMART choice.

profile:
Imperial Roofs were awarded the Vaughan Citizen Readers Choice Award in 2011

In 1968 my father founded Cel Marchildon Roofing, which has grown into the company we have today.  Through commitment to excellence in our workmanship and materials we have built our reputation of TOTAL CUSTOMER SATISFACTION by providing our customers with the BEST ROOFING SYSTEM that will accommodate their needs and budget.  We will provide you, our valued customer, with a detailed assessment that will outline the specific requirements for your home. 

Our expert staff is committed to providing you with the BEST ROOFING EXPERIENCE available in the GTA.  All workers are covered by WORKERS COMPENSATION.  Our company is fully LICENSED AND INSURED to provide you with a WORRY FREE ROOFING EXPERIENCE.  We DO NOT USE ROOFING SUB-CONTRACTORS.  All work is performed by our expert employees. 

This may or may not be your first time purchasing a new roof, however we would like to outline some of the key factors in our operating process:

?	Provide a copy of our Insurance Certificate
?	Provide a copy of Workplace Insurance Safety Board Certificate upon request
?	Provide a copy of our Operating License 
?	Protect your home and surrounding area from falling debris
?	Tear off all old shingles to the roof deck
?	Inspect the wood deck for rotting and warping areas
?	Install eave protection to all insulated eaves 
?	Install name brand shingles with your choice 25 years to limited lifetime guarantee
?	Install proper ventilation to the roof (1sq ft for every 300 sq ft of attic floor area) 
?	Install new metal flashing where needed or refurbish to “new” standards
?	Install closed valleys with aluminum underneath to ensure maximum protection 
?	Full property clean up using magnetic sweeps and trailers to ensure no driveway damage
?	All employees are Fall Safety accredited and Crew Chief First Aid and CPR trained

Services We Provide:
*Asphalt Shingle Replacement
*Gutters, Soffit & Fascia
*Siding - Vinyl, Aluminum
*Leaf Screen for Eavestroughs
*Rooftop Snow & Ice Dam Removal
*Roof Repairs
*Roof Evaluations
*Cedar Shakes
*Slate Roofs
*Insurance Claims
*Ventilation Upgrades

profile:
Gutter Force was started in an observation that eavestrough cleaning was a hazardous job that if done differently could make it safer and avoid people falling off ladders and seriously hurting themselves.

We have evolved into a unique specialized home service company in eavestroughing . We have three primary services that we provide; Eavestrough repair ,eavestrough replacement or installation,  Aluminum Soffit and fascia exterior makeovers.

Gutter Force is under professional management by team of experts is knowledgeable,skilled and dedicated. We pride ourselves in excellent customer satisfaction.


Gutter Force offer eavestrough installation and repair as well as gutter and downpipe repair or replacement,downspout disconnection, soffit and fascia installation, ice dam removal and more in Toronto and area.

profile:
Leafguard is available in Canada

Trades by Jack is proud to offer this fantastic product to help you. Avoid the messy work involved in dealing with your gutters and eavestroughs.

Say goodbye to the dangerous and unpleasant job of climbing up to your roof to clean out your gutters once and for all, without the expense of paying someone else to do it.

Gutters capture the rainwater from your roof and carry it safely to the ground, away from your foundation, where it can cause serious damage. Ordinary gutters capture leaves, twigs and other organic debris that causes them to clog and overflow during rainstorms.

 •LeafGuard’s patented design causes rainwater to flow around its curved hood and into the gutter, keeping leaves and debris out.
 •LeafGuard Brand Gutters are guaranteed not to clog for as long as you own your home, or Gutter Depot will clean your gutters for free.
 •LeafGuard Gutters are made to fit any home in a variety of colours. Best of all they are made out durable materials, designed to last as long as you have a roof.
 
 Call Us for Free Estimate!

profile:
Topflight Aluminum is dedicated to providing quality construction and exceptional customer service. We strive to build lifelong relationships with our customers and to exceed your expectations, in every aspect of the job, from start to finish.
We’ve helped thousands of people improve the look and quality of their homes and businesses. We are proud to serve Toronto (GTA), Etobicoke, North York, Scarborough, Vaughan, Richmond Hill, Markham, Stouffville, King City, Aurora, York Region, Mississauga, Oakville, Hamilton residents with expert craftsmanship and professionalism. We pride ourselves on being able to exceed the expectations of our customers.

•	WHY TopFlight Aluminum?

1.	Quality first, Speed second
We all like our issues to be resolved efficiently when contacting a company, but what will make you use Topflight Aluminum again and again? There is only one answer. The quality of the service!

2.	Great Customer Service
We understand that building or remodeling a home is a major investment, so for us it is important that our customers feel valued. Topflight Aluminum pays special attention to what our clients want, we remember the details no matter how insignificant and deliver quality services at all times.

3.	Top Quality Materials
Apart from good workmanship and top-grade professionals handling your building project, the best quality of materials we use will be next most important factor in determining the outcome of your building.

4.	Warranty

Building your dream house shouldn’t be a nightmare! That’s why we only use guaranteed products and materials with 30- to 50-year warranties. Additionally, all of our work comes with workmanship warranty. Whether you are replacing or repairing, Topflight Aluminum can always meet your needs!

OUR MISSION
Our goal is simple… To perform for our customers the highest level of quality construction services at fair and market competitive prices. We aim to maintain the highest levels of professionalism, integrity, honesty and fairness in our relationships with our suppliers, subcontractors, professional associates and customers.





GET A FREE QUOTE
No unexpected charges —see exactly what your home needs with a free estimate.

profile:
Hello, 

My name is Tommy Hrstic and I am the owner of Sunrise Aluminum.  I have 20 years of hands on experience in the industry, and Sunrise Aluminum has been serving the greater Toronto area and beyond for more than 15 years and counting.  We specialize in seamless aluminum eaves trough installations, along with large square downspouts which has been the industry standard for the vast majority of residential homes and many commercial properties over the past decade.  We have remained a small company and all your interactions will be be with me directly and all our work is done or overseen by me personally to ensure the highest quality and customer satisfaction.  We use only the highest quality materials and aluminum purchased from reputable suppliers (Gentek and Kaycan) with many colours and materials to chose from.  

At Sunrise Aluminum we have always placed customer satisfaction as our number one priority, and have had continued success mostly thanks to their positive feedback and referrals.  With us you can always expect top quality product and workmanship for a fair price, and you can always count on us to complete your job in a timely manner as we pride ourselves in our commitment to punctuality, efficiency, and reliability.  

Contact us for a free estimate and consultation, we look forward to working with you.


Tommy Hrstic
Sunrise Aluminum
